data.description: Introducing 2211 Granite Park Lane, a truly exceptional property that combines luxury living with convenience. This spacious home offers five bedrooms and three and a half bathrooms, ensuring comfort for your family and guests. Its strategic location near highways 59 and 36 makes commuting a breeze.    Inside, you'll find a host of desirable features, including a game room and media room for entertainment, as well as an office for your work or study needs. Custom paint adds a personalized touch, creating a unique atmosphere throughout the home.    Step outside to discover a covered patio overlooking a spacious backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. With its blend of modern amenities, ample space, and a prime location, this property is the ideal place to call home.
